A newly renovated family home with great privacy throughout all windows.

THE PROPERTY
Double Brick construction provides
- comfort temperature throughout the year
- block out noises for more privacy & comfort

NORTH ORIENTATION

- Two full bathrooms with a bathtub in each
- Open kitchen with Gas cooking
- Ducted Air conditioning
- Security car park & Intercom

Just a moment's walk to the shopping village & railway station


THE SUBURB
Surrounded by Sydney's most prestigious public and private schools.

Notable residents like David Campese, Mel Gibson, Hugh Jackman, John Toohey and many more were born, raised or schooled in this suburb.

The local shopping village brings the boutique element to this busy, friendly North-Sydney-style neighbourhood.

Convenient transport to Central, Hornsby, Newcastle and North Shore.
